'''克卜勒186f'''（{{lang-en|'''Kepler-186f'''}}）是一顆環繞[[紅矮星|紅矮星]][[克卜勒186|克卜勒186]]的[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]，距離地球約492光年<ref name="NYT-20140417">{{cite news |last=Chang |first=Kenneth |title=Scientists Find an ‘Earth Twin,’ or Maybe a Cousin |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/18/science/space/scientists-find-an-earth-twin-or-maybe-a-cousin.html |date=17 April 2014 |work=[[紐約時報|New York Times]] |accessdate=17 April 2014 |archive-date=2019-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009121850/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/18/science/space/scientists-find-an-earth-twin-or-maybe-a-cousin.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AP-20140417">{{cite news |last=Chang |first=Alicia |title=Astronomers spot most Earth-like planet yet |url=http://apnews.excite.com/article/20140417/DAD832V81.html |date=17 April 2014 |work=[[美聯社|AP News]] |accessdate=17 April 2014 |archive-date=2014-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418172517/http://apnews.excite.com/article/20140417/DAD832V81.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC-20140417">{{cite news |last=Morelle |first=Rebecca |title='Most Earth-like planet yet' spotted by Kepler |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-27054366 |date=17 April 2014 |work=[[BBC新聞|BBC News]] |accessdate=17 April 2014 |archive-date=2014-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418172858/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-27054366 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該行星是第一顆在太陽以外恆星旁發現的[[適居帶|適居帶]]內半徑與地球相若的系外行星。[[NASA|NASA]] 的[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]以[[系外行星偵測法#凌日法|凌日法]]偵測到克卜勒186f和另外4顆距離母恆星更近，且半徑都稍大於地球的系外行星<ref name="AP-20140417"/>。天文學家耗時3年分析資料找到了克卜勒186f存在的訊號<ref name="SETI2014">{{cite web
